data.description: This lovely 4 bedroom 2 bath home is nestled in the heart of Clay. It is located on a quite dead end street and is mintues from Clays wonderful schools. Fenced in yard that is great for family gatherings or a place to let the dogs run. The home has a new covered back deck that can entertain the whole family. New roof installed within the last year. HVAC replaced in 2017. This home has years of worry free maintenance with these major items recently taken care of. Dont miss out on this gem!
